

	 
       GOODBYE   goodbye.  a simple word  yet meaningful  a simple word  yet dreadful  to me.   so,just go   without saying it  would you?  infact,just go   without saying a thing  can you?.   it hurts  listening to you  saying goodbye  to me.   so,just leave  without a word  without looking back  without goodbye  just leave.   the light of my life  just slipped from my hands  i lose the battle  i lost  you.   so,just stand up  turn around and walk away  without saying   goodbye.   
     
    
